title: A man playing a trombone in an orange baseball cap and shirt, at the UVa Library
shortDescription: A man in an orange baseball cap blowing into a large silver trumpet. He is wearing a necklace made of small round beads with a larger pendant. The background consists of drums and a cymbal. The image has GPS coordinates not available.
longDescription: The image captures a moment at the UVa Library where a man in an orange baseball cap is passionately playing a large silver trombone. He is standing in front of a drum set, which includes a bass drum, a tom-tom, and a cymbal. The man is wearing a necklace made of small round beads with a larger pendant around his neck. The image does not provide any information about the location or time when this photo was taken. It only shows the man's dedication to his music and the musical instruments he plays.
